		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="429" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">守望者蓄力，放出15个螺旋弹，该弹瞄准玩家后直线攻击，每个均造成<span color="#99ff87">50%,<br/>25%,12.5%,5%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
